---
title: Smart Turkey and Mushroom Stew with Roasted Potatoes and Spinach
description: This hearty dinner has all the flavours of a traditional stew, but on the lighter side. Turkey, potatoes, thyme, mushrooms and spinach are featured in this dish that's sure to warm your soul and your stomach.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-dinde-et-de-champignons-c5155c38.jpg
